{"tid":1156952,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"在座各位都係垃圾","createTime":"2019-05-16T02:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T06:03:42.000Z","uid":238673,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"453b5e8c30929c7fc584b074319d25ce5e748aef","tid":1156952,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"井底之蛙<br />\n講最正打鬥明顯大部分人睇得太少<br />\n基本三大特撮打鬥已經可以同大部分動作片平起平坐<br />\n點解有人覺得特撮2個字有問題？唔通我睇過邊邊套幪面超人/戰隊邊集邊個鏡頭最正都講你知？仲有啲冷門野好多人都無聽過井底之蛙又搵唔到片點講？<br />\n再講，唔通我順住成龍李連杰丹哥tony jaa洪金寶劉家良大大小小通通睇過哂又同你班無知交代？<br />\n啲死癲狗專咬人都係葡萄啫<br />\n少少人認咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想一下打全部人，感覺好大部分都同某些癲狗一樣咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9169641303075ee22fc23c257872778fa6950d5","tid":1156952,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"如果真係咁嘅話點解你啲post冇正皮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1a913c333b8070fdf23334ccbf5b097daced71","tid":1156952,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9169641303075ee22fc23c257872778fa6950d5","tid":1156952,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"如果真係咁嘅話點解你啲post冇正皮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"因為在座各位都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會識睇正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c94c60344fb6fe020fca1630f56987ee083bc1a","tid":1156952,"uid":200550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd1a913c333b8070fdf23334ccbf5b097daced71","tid":1156952,"uid":238673,"like":0,"di